<h1>AbeGaming</h1>

<p>A few helper tools for my gaming friends. See the <a href="about">About page</a> for more information and useful links.</p>

<h2>Available Tools</h2>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> Currently all tools are in <span class="text-monospace">BETA</span> stage,
 which means <a href="contact">feedback</a> is very welcome!</p>
<ul>
    <li><a href="ftpbattle">For The People - Battle Calculator</a>:
        Single result and/or stats for the legendary "For The People" boardgame by
        <a href="https://www.e-markherman.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mark Herman</a>
        and <a href="https://www.gmtgames.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GMT Games</a>.<br />
        <i>Roll the dice to get a single result for a given battle,
        or calculate the probabilities of victory, distribution of casualties,
        and other relevant expected values for a given battle setup.</i><br />
        <i>It could help planning your next move.</i>
    </li>
    <li><a href="pogbattle">Paths of Glory - Battle Calculator</a>:
        Same tool for the just-as-legendary "Paths of Glory" boardgame by Ted Raicer and
        <a href="https://www.gmtgames.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GMT Games</a>.
    </li>
</ul>

<div class="alert alert-info mt-4">
    <strong>📱 Tip:</strong> You can <a href="install">install this as an app</a> on your phone or desktop for offline access!
</div>

